{"tid":1795202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（FreedomHK G20)#meiwithhongkong T恤已於光時上架! !!!","createTime":"2019-12-23T16:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T02:01:25.000Z","uid":18245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb5c99c9195e3bebe775d706e582e7fd6dbe321","tid":1795202,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkuXVS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkuXVS9.jpg&h=8333857b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我雖勢弱言輕 但決不虛作無聲<br />\n<br />\nFreedomHK G20團隊10月時為香港電競選手聰哥受暴雪無理懲罰「光復香港，時代革命」而製作嘅#meiwithhongkong T恤已於光時上架! <br />\n<br />\n光時有幸得到FreedomHK G20團隊授權印製#meiwithhongkong T恤，令光時支持者可以與手足同行。<br />\n<br />\nT恤用咗210g棉做，質素唔錯架😌<br />\n暫時限定只出售800件！<br />\n貨品傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SkilL0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SkilL0&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=3aeee2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SkilL0</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 提提大家由即日起到12月31號係光時購物超過$1000（禮品咭除外），即可收到由光時設計師及攝影師設計嘅年曆咭一套。<br />\n（名額有限，送完即止。）<br />\n<br />\n光時<br />\n支援義士，幫襯光時<br />\n<br />\n#香港有光自由有時<br />\n#光時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=172878080769729&amp;id=107180774006127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D172878080769729%26id%3D107180774006127&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=02353cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=172878080769729&amp;id=107180774006127</a>"},{"pid":"e21d47c07a4718573f68463a8b593b3a8d34338e","tid":1795202,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"made in 邊度？"},{"pid":"e6dac3419b277534db647a0aa3f3f95662aac23d","tid":1795202,"uid":13972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5